  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in the clay tajine over medium heat.",
    "add the chopped onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "add the minced garlic and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "add the bone-in chicken thighs and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "add the chopped basil, ground cumin, ground coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "mix well to combine.",
    "add the chicken broth and white wine.",
    "bring the mixture to a boil, then cover the tajine with its lid.",
    "transfer the tajine to the oven and bake at 375°f for 45 minutes.",
    "remove the tajine from the oven and let it rest for 10 minutes before serving.",
    "serve the chicken and sauce hot, garnished with additional chopped basil if desired."
  ],
